description:
It’s not almost paradise, it IS Paradise! Finally! The Broads chat the first episode of this, sure to be, drama filled season! They chat about their love for Katie and Tayshia, both giving their date card to Wills, Chris Harrison’s jeans, Blake....ughhhhhh, Clay’s blocking Bekah, Stagecoach shenanigans, and much more!
